@startuml
title Add Citation + Snapshot (Trust Layer v1)

actor Author as A
participant "DRF API" as API
participant "Trust Layer" as Trust
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Background Jobs" as Jobs

A -> API: POST /api/posts/{id}/citations {url, title?}
API -> Trust: add_citation(post_id, url, metadata)
Trust -> DB: INSERT citation(post_id, url, accessed_at=now())
DB --> Trust: citation_id
Trust -> Jobs: enqueue snapshot_fetch(citation_id)
Trust --> API: 201 Created (citation)
API --> A: citation

== Async snapshot ==
Jobs -> Trust: snapshot_fetch(citation_id)
Trust -> DB: SELECT citation.url
Trust -> Trust: fetch url, extract metadata/text\n(hash content)
Trust -> DB: INSERT source_snapshot(...)\nUPDATE citation.snapshot_ref
Trust --> Jobs: ok

@enduml

